task.summary: Updated Q learning for the agent. Parameter used here are epsilon and alpha. The epsilon is used for action choosing and alpha for learning. Epsilon is a function of trial numbers and alpha keeps constant 0.5 here which means taking average of learned result and new actions.
Optimized Q learning with a new epsilon function. Changed the state space.
